<a href="/mobile/articles/17363.html" class="com-grid-key-article">
	<div class="grid-key-article-hd">
		<div class="imgcover">
				<img class="pic" src="/system/articles/articleshows/17363/medium/17363.jpg?1447158659" alt="《007：幽灵党》找了吉尼斯，得到“影史最大规模爆炸”认证">
		</div>
	</div>
